CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 24, 1955, pg. 13 reads: "Who'll Win Wolf Shoe Free Trip? - Mary Dee, disc jockey of Radio Station WHOD, joins Morris Wolf of Wolf's Shoe Store in guessing who will receive Wolf's free vacation trip to Florida. The lucky winners will be posted in Wolf's window at 1710 Centre Avenue until Oct. 6 - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: WHOD radio disc jockey Mary Dee drawing out of a box in front of promotion for "Win a Free Vacation for Two at Booker Terrace in Florida" at Wolf's shoe store, Centre Avenue, Hill District
